io.permazen.kv.rocksdb

Class RocksDBKVDatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.permazen.kv.mvcc.SnapshotKVDatabase
      • io.permazen.kv.rocksdb.RocksDBKVDatabase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KVDatabase

    public class RocksDBKVDatabase
extends SnapshotKVDatabase
    KVDatabase implementation based on a RocksDBAtomicKVStore, providing concurrent transactions and linearizable ACID semantics.

    Key watches are supported.
